channel.title: Looking for a team to make an RSPS
channel.description: I need help making an RSPS. I swear to you, i have been trying to make one for about a year or 2 now but my computer always finds a way to mess it up. Anyways I have came to the decision that i may need a helper or coder to help me with making the server. If you can successfully help me make it and get it running, then i'll make you co-owner. Anyways, if you want to help me, you could either pm me your Skype name or comment it below. One more thing i want to add before posting this is that i am a very cooperative and loyal person.
